name: Travelling Connectors - 01
description: These kinectic systems build on my exploration of constellations and are made of nodes and connections. Various rules govern the nodes' movement and their choice to form a connection. The rules themselves are 'simple' but complex behaviour emerges - geometric shapes that look designed but are, in fact, unpredictable. This is my first ever NFT | Amy Goodchild | Twitter - @amygoodchild | Instagram - @amy_goodchild | www.amygoodchild.com | p5js, 1080x1080, 0:30
